---
import Stack from '../../components/primitives/Stack.astro';
---

<Stack gap="12">
  <p class="ds-type-body-l-tall">
    Navigation data lives in a single module so Rail, sidebar TOC, mobile bar, and overlays stay aligned. See
    <code class="ds-type-code-l-tall">src/design-system/lib/navigation.ts</code>.
  </p>
  <ul class="ds-type-body-l-tall" style="margin: 0; padding-left: var(--spacing-24); color: var(--foreground-secondary);">
    <li>Each item: id, label, optional icon, destination, group, priority, order, optional children.</li>
    <li>Primary items surface in compact patterns; overflow uses overlay / “More”.</li>
    <li>Do not redefine labels or routes per pattern — import from the shared model.</li>
  </ul>
</Stack>
